Key Match Events: Paolo Banchero scored 34 points in his return after missing 34 games with a torn right oblique
Others: Orlando Magic lost to Milwaukee Bucks 109-106
Giannis Antetokounmpo led all scorers with 41 points
Jalen Suggs, Gary Harris, and Jett Howard were out due to injuries for the Magic
Cole Anthony scored 18 points with seven rebounds for the Magic
Tristan da Silva tallied 16 points and 10 rebounds for the Magic
Anthony Black added 15 off the bench for the Magic
Orlando dropped to 22–18 with the defeat
Bobby Portis and Khris Middleton each added 11 points off the bench for the Bucks
Damian Lillard followed with 29 points with seven assists, four rebounds and three steals for the Bucks
Milwaukee improved to 20–16 with the win
